text: Tessa ter Sluis (born 16 January 1995 in Sint Willebrord) is a Dutch professional squash player. As of August 2020, she was ranked number 63 in the world. She is in the Netherlands women's national squash team. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch female squash players Category:Sportspeople from Rucphen Category:Competitors at the 2017 World Games
